Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:28.82,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(303,318)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Springtime
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:32.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:35.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stop my heart from dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:41.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Crying and laughing, we never forget our memories together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:52.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Finding your true self
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:55.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And becoming an adult is difficult work
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:58.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I can forget for now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:01.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The night is waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:06.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As our hearts beat excitedly in rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:08.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And we frolic about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:12.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I nearly realize
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The feelings I want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if we are afraid of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:23.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You cannot move if you remain empty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:29.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all right if we have fun, so let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:33.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I forget all my troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:36.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and dance the night away with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:43.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll become someone more wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:47.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This endless Golden Time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The distance between us as you approach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:53.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Neither closes nor widens
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:57.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll treasure this even if it's the long way around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:14.55,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(260,52)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Fukurai University Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm Tada Banri of the law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:24.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Show me your student ID.\NAnd tell me why you were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not used to living in Tokyo, so I got lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:30.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I got on the wrong train, and when I finally reached the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I couldn't find the exit and was running in circles...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.42,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(148,168)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Student ID
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.42,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(192,200)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Name: Tada Banri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.42,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(147,234)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Affiliation: Fukurai Private University
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.42,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(267,264)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Law School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:42.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That concludes this year's entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:48.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}New students, please head to your department's building for orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:57.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This spring, I moved from my home in Shizuoka to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:02.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I made my long-anticipated college debut,\NTokyo debut, and solitary living debut...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:07.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I started it all by being late to the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can really do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A lot of parents are here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So we head to the college now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:30.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's one stop away on the subway, or a fifteen-minute walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How should we get to the college?\NWant to take the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Won't the subway be crowded?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not that far if we take a shortcut. Let's walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, have you decided which club you're joining?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:52.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wonder what kinds of clubs there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even I think I'm being suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's so hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Want to get some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think there's a convenience store up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:21.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She said, "let's meet in front of the college."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? We'd better hurry, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead. We're not buying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:32.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She said she'll be there in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:38.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That will be 150 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:03.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you a law school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:11.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't know the way to the college...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I followed those girls because they seemed to know the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but they went into the convenience store..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:22.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I thought I'd better follow them, and bought ice cream, too..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can call me Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm Yanagisawa Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can call me Mitsuo or Yana or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:40.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You from Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Shizuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What about you... Yana... Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm living on my own, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:48.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looks like this is the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This must be the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:06.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know... I was late this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:10.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't have anyone to talk to until just now, so I was kinda discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:14.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It seemed like other people were already making friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so I felt even more alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:21.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I attended the same university affiliate since elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so I've never felt so out of place before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:26.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,An affiliate? To a different university?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:31.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, from elementary to high school. Dainohara's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:33.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're kidding!\NThat's a really prestigious school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why did you come to this college?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You definitely should've kept riding the escalator there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Was there some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:49.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry! I shouldn't be asking someone\NI just met so many insensitive questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not at all. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's just a long story...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The short version is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:59.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I got into some trouble with the opposite sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:02.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The opposite sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:06.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just got sick of people living in narrow worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:10.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted to turn over a new leaf in a new environment in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So basically, you had an argument with your girlfriend...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She wasn't... my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She was, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:22.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,a disaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:27.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, like a calamity...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A calamity...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're a college student now, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I removed the thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:17.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're an idiot, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you think you could run away from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:23.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'll be mine forever, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who was that? What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:48.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A lovers' quarrel right in front of the college?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:51.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That guy with the roses is a new student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is he doing right after the entrance ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:09:00.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My college life ended on its first day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:03.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Yana-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:06.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:08.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here. Take one if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Is this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take one, take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Th-thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:18.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:22.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought we might be able to play it off like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:22.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take one. There's plenty more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:31.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}We're handing out roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:39.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}In college, you have mandatory courses and electives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:44.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}In law school, many electives will be available to you starting from your first year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:47.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}so be sure to choose carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please turn to the first page of your documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.09,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(284,347)}Kaga Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:55.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Your mandatory courses are general education courses and physical education.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:54.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.49,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(101,344)}we've known each other since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Even if you have enough elective credits,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:59.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Her dad runs a huge hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:00.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}if you do not have sufficient credits from mandatory courses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He knows my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}you will not be able to move up or graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.60,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(183,347)}Heiress of a big hospital, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:08.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Because of this, we strongly recommend you take as many credits as you can in your first two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:07.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We attended the same schools from kindergarten to high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.84,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(78,347)}we were supposed to attend the same college...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:15.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}In general, your deadlines for reports and papers will be stricter than they were in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:15.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you came to this university because you didn't want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}so be sure to turn things in on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:20.31,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(195,346)}I'm arguing with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:20.31,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(200,310)}Yeah. And because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:22.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Mandatory courses have already been scheduled,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:23.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They won't send me any money, and I'm having all kinds of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:29.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}but electives will be scheduled according to the academic programs you set for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:27.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You must have really wanted to get away from Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Terrifyingly enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.93,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(188,311)}she decided we'd get married
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.93,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(245,343)}when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}We have also distributed documents explaining the courses,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Without consulting me! On her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}so please consult them when considering which classes to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That just sounds like a typical romantic story to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:45.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Additionally, the registration period is at the beginning of the term, and each class will hold guidance sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't understand!\NYou don't understand at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You saw what happened earlier, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just because I wouldn't go to college with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You may attend these freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,she's the kind of girl who'll wait for me at my entrance ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Class sizes are limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so she can slap me in the face with roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:54.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}and students are sometimes unable to take the courses they want due to over-enrollment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She really is a calamity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know about a calamity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko has her own perfect plan.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}In these cases, students who {\c&HFFFFFF&}registered first are given priority,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:03.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}so we recommend you sign up for courses you wish to take early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The only reason she attaches herself to me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:03.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,is because she wants her life to go according to that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.73,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(227,347)}If I try to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:08.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}However, if you sign up for too many courses in an attempt to take as many credits as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Mitsuo, that's wrong!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.33,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(182,347)}"Mitsuo, that's not in my plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}you will experience great difficulty during exams and when reports are due,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Mitsuo, do as I say!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:14.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}leading to problems acquiring your credits, so please be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.80,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(177,345)}"Mitsuo, blah blah blah blah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.34,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(208,346)}"Mitsuo, blah blah blah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.78,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(121,345)}"Mitsuo, blah blah blah blah BLAH!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? She wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She was more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I removed the thorns!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Mitsuo, do blah blah blah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Mitsuo, don't do blah blah blah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Mitsuo, don't you think blah blah blah?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? She's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:55.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop chatting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:58.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This concludes your orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:06.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Starting today, be sure to act with the awareness that you are students of this department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:19.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing in this university...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:38.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...in this department...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...in this orientation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Those are the guys who were handing out roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're standing out a lot on their first day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san, you're being too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm conforming to your desires, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm attending this university, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My, you look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll be able to study together for four more years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-what about your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,According to your life plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,weren't you going to stay on the escalator,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,study French literature, and spend your third year studying abroad in France?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:15.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then you would build a career in fashion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's true I did need to make some modifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But it was no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:25.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I don't enjoy my college life with you,\NMitsuo, there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:30.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How did you know I applied to this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:35.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know my father makes donations to various universities, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was easy enough to figure out where you wanted to go using my connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:43.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo, aren't you happy that I'm so devoted to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're happy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But you're actually happy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:54.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I SAID I'M NOT HAPPY!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I applied to a different school to get away from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and now it's all ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:09.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo is one of those famous types.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tsu-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:11.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tsun-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:12.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tsunde-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tsundere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:19.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you Mitsuo's new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... ah... I'm Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm from Shizuoka, and I just met Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:28.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait, Mitsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Yana-san! Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let me help you pick those up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is she really a college student?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:04.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Were those your friends? That was pretty crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It certainly was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're both so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what you meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll be friends with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:19.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looking at pretty people makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:22.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whether they're boys or girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:26.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really? I guess Yana-san's pretty handsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess she's a little unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm Oka Chinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Chinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See you, Tada-kun, I hope we can be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's up? Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's Tada-kun! We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:09.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Friends, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.40,Dialogue10,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(495,192)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Shogi Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.40,Dialogue14,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(94,232)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.40,Dialogue14,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(69,284)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.40,Dialogue10,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(83,321)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.61,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(369,82)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Wrestling Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:20.33,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(55,118)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Daytime Napping
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:20.33,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(77,145)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Association
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your admission!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you interested in comedy?!\NWe put on student shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:44.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We are the glee club!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:49.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You look like you enjoy sleeping outdoors!\NThe outdoor club's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're the tea club!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're especially recruiting boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:58.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Drink some, drink some. Drink, drink, drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:16:59.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Way to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:09.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was so bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:12.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, you. Would you like to join the Latin music club?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You won't get away that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you want to run, you'll have to get past us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, come on. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, sorr-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:47.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry. Was I too rough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,N-no... Um, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you a first year?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:59.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Uh, yes. I'm Tada Banri from the law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:03.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Linda"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My actual name is Hayashida
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1BFEF9&}It's written as "forest" and "rice field."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But "forest" is also written as "Rin," hence Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The club recruitment is a war zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I always carry these just for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Really, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:23.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's a senpai's job to look after younger students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, which club are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm in the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I won't try to force you to join, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:37.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This must be more than a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you ever need anything, you can come talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm in the law school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:42.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:50.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your lipstick... It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:06.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm in Tokyo... I'm really here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:12.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I can be reborn as a new person here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can meet new friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.82,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(231,231)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}TADA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,stay in a new place,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:22.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and live in a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:28.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's so much fun, and I'm so happy and satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:31.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if I'm sad or lonely or make mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,everything shines like gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:39.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I can lead a blindingly bright life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:44.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I keep living life like that,\NI'll probably fall in love eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:54.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to feel like I could give my whole heart to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:57.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can have that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:00.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I can have that love...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:15.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, you're that boy from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,T-Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:26.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for Mitsuo.\NHe should come by this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:28.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you just call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He won't answer his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo's never honest with himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:37.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But that's what makes him cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:44.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri? Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm still at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Listen, about those documents I threw...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, those. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:56.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo! You're still at school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko?! What are you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm heading there now! Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:10.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I forgot to return your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:20.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you. I hope we can continue to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:24.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:27.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.82,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(274,214)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Received Call:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.82,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(303,253)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Hospital{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:52.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said I'd wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:19.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In one hand in the sweetened cafe latte I love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:23.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The moment I smiled I could smell love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:28.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to wear my cherry-colored dress perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:33.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My heart beats quietly as I rush to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,(Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:37.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watch out for that sweet trap
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:39.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,(Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:42.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll whisper to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:44.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}(Hey, I'm a little anxious)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.49,0:22:46.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, I long for this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:50.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How should I smile when I see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:54.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Pretty love, pretty love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Under the sky, under sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:00.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's hold hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:05.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't be honest about my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:10.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But pull me along by my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:41.04,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(55,413)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Lonely Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:29.54,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(214,374)}You're so stupid, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:33.04,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(126,374)}I would never say, "Blah blah blah blah."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:37.38,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(192,373)}I found Mitsuo! Wait, Mitsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:40.21,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(215,371)}Blah blah blah blah blah!
